### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("jwt", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### Listar precios (scope organization)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Crear o actualizar precio (requiere profileId o itemId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profileId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "itemId": null,
  "unitPrice": 150.00,
  "validFrom": null,
  "validTo": null,
  "notes": "Precio especial para perfil IPE 300"
}

### Eliminar precio
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/prices/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Listar facturas
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Crear factura borrador
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

customerName=Cliente Ejemplo&customerVat=ESB12345678

> {%
    client.global.set("invoiceId", response.body.id);
%}

### Obtener factura por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Anadir linea a factura
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "lineNumber": 1,
  "profileId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "itemId": null,
  "description": "IPE 300 - 12m",
  "quantity": 10,
  "unitPrice": 145.00,
  "vatRate": 21.00
}

> {%
    client.global.set("invoiceLineId", response.body.id);
%}

### Ver lineas de factura
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Eliminar linea de factura
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/lines/{{invoiceLineId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Emitir factura (DRAFT a ISSUED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/issue
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Marcar como pagada (ISSUED a PAID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/pay
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### Cancelar factura (solo desde DRAFT o ISSUED)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/billing/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}
